&lt;p&gt;The word &amp;#39;punctilious&amp;#39; has been spelt here incorrectly. The meaning of the words is as follows:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Staunch =&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:helvetica neue,arial,liberation sans,freesans,sans-serif&quot;&gt;loyal; faithful; dependable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Punctilious =&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:arial,sans-serif&quot;&gt;showing great attention to detail or correct behaviour.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Furtive =&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:helvetica neue,arial,liberation sans,freesans,sans-serif&quot;&gt;hidden and secret &lt;/span&gt;Quagmire =&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:helvetica neue,arial,liberation sans,freesans,sans-serif&quot;&gt;marsh; bog.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;Spending a lot of ineffectual time and energy&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;Chasing one&amp;#39;s tail&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot; is an &lt;strong&gt;idiomatic expression&lt;/strong&gt; that means &lt;strong&gt;to spend a lot of time and energy in a futile or ineffective way, usually in an attempt to achieve a goal that is difficult or impossible to attain&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;It is often used in the &lt;strong&gt;context &lt;/strong&gt;of someone who is trying to accomplish something but is not making any progress.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In the given &lt;strong&gt;sentence&lt;/strong&gt;, he is trying to sell the product but he has not been able to meet his target. It implies that he is spending a lot of time and energy in a futile or ineffective way in order to sell the product, but not making any progress.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thus, &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;option 2 &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;is the correct answer.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;Chasing one&amp;#39;s tail&lt;/span&gt;&amp;quot; एक &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;idiomatic expression&lt;/span&gt; है जिसका अर्थ है &lt;strong&gt;व्यर्थ या अप्रभावी तरीके से बहुत समय और ऊर्जा खर्च करना, आमतौर पर एक ऐसे लक्ष्य को प्राप्त करने के प्रयास में जो प्राप्त करना कठिन या असंभव है।&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;Chasm&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Let&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;us&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;explore&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;given options&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;Volcano&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;a mountain or hill, typically conical, having a crater or vent through which lava, rock fragments, hot vapour, and gas are or have been erupted from the earth&amp;#39;s crust&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;Tremor&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;a slight earthquake&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Chasm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;a deep fissure in the earth&amp;#39;s surface&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Earthquake&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;a sudden violent shaking of the ground, typically causing great destruction, as a result of movements within the earth&amp;#39;s crust or volcanic action&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 3&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Please&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fret&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;(verb)&lt;/strong&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to be worried and unhappy about something&amp;nbsp;(किसी विषय में चिंतित और दुखी होना)&lt;/strong&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;​&lt;u&gt;E.g.&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;-&amp;nbsp;Don&amp;#39;t &lt;strong&gt;fret&lt;/strong&gt; - I&amp;#39;m sure he&amp;#39;s OK.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(verb)&lt;/strong&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to make somebody happy&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;(&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;किसी को ख़ुश या प्रसन्&amp;zwj;न करना)&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;​&lt;u&gt;E.g.&lt;/u&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;There&amp;rsquo;s just no &lt;strong&gt;pleasing&lt;/strong&gt; some people.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Please&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bother&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(verb)&lt;/strong&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to disturb, annoy or worry somebody&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;(&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;परेशान, तंग या चिंतित करना)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;​&lt;u&gt;E.g.&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m sorry to &lt;strong&gt;bother&lt;/strong&gt; you, but could I speak to you for a moment?&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Worry&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(verb)&lt;/strong&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;to think that something bad might happen or has happened&amp;nbsp;(किसी दुर्घटना की आशंका से चिंतित होना)&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;​&lt;u&gt;E.g.&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;There&amp;rsquo;s nothing to &lt;strong&gt;worry&lt;/strong&gt; about.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Disturb&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(verb)&lt;/strong&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to interrupt what someone is doing (किसी के कुछ काम करते समय उसमें बाधा पहुँचाना)&lt;/strong&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;​&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;E.g.&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Please don&amp;#39;t &lt;strong&gt;disturb&lt;/strong&gt; your sister - she&amp;#39;s trying to do her homework.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The correct answer is &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;undiminished&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The word &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;undiminished&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot; means not reduced or lessened. (अक्षुण्ण)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Even though false allegations were made, the judge&amp;#39;s reputation did not decrease in the legal community.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The other options: &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;damaged&lt;/strong&gt;,&amp;quot; &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;illegal&lt;/strong&gt;,&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;uncertain&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot; do not fit the context as appropriately.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;​Therefore, the correct answer is &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Option 1&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complete Sentence:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;The judge&amp;rsquo;s standing in the legal community, though shaken by false allegations of wrongdoing, remained &lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;undiminished&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Damaged (क्षतिग्रस्त)&lt;/strong&gt;: means harmed or injured.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Illegal (अवैध)&lt;/strong&gt;: means not allowed by law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Uncertain (अनिश्चित)&lt;/strong&gt;: means not known or definite.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is: &lt;strong&gt;muffled&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;muffled&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; means a sound that is not loud because of being obstructed in some way; muted. (मंद)

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example: &lt;/strong&gt;The thick walls muffled the sound of the traffic outside.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Hence, we can infer that the horn of the car ahead was muffled by the resistance of the thick air.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Therefore, the correct answer is: &lt;strong&gt;muffled&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here are the other options explained along with their Hindi meanings and example sentences:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dim &lt;/strong&gt;(&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;मंद&lt;/span&gt;): Lacking brightness or clarity.

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; The room was dimly lit by a single bulb.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Faint &lt;/strong&gt;(&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;मंद&lt;/span&gt;): Barely perceptible.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example: &lt;/strong&gt;She heard a faint sound coming from the basement.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mute&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;मूक&lt;/span&gt;): Silent or unable to speak.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; The remote control can mute the television sound.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&lt;strong&gt; &amp;quot;indomitable.&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Indomitable&amp;quot; &lt;/strong&gt;is an adjective that describes a person who possesses unwavering determination, resilience, and persistence, and doesn&amp;#39;t easily give up or get defeated.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In this context, it perfectly describes Nancy&amp;#39;s spirit that helped her overcome numerous personal and professional challenges - suggesting her spirit couldn&amp;#39;t be subdued or overcome.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore, considering the contextual meaning, the correct word is &amp;#39;indomitable&amp;#39;.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The sentence could be:&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;Nancy&amp;#39;s indomitable spirit helped her overcome numerous personal and professional challenges.&amp;quot;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Option 1.&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;Vacillating&amp;#39;: means indecisiveness or being unsure, which contradicts the idea of someone overcoming challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;Weak&amp;#39;: presents the opposite notion of someone overcoming challenges.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;It means lack of strength or resilience.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;Frail&amp;#39;: similar to &amp;#39;weak&amp;#39;, shows a lack of physical or mental strength.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&lt;strong&gt; &amp;quot;influential.&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Influential&amp;#39; &lt;/strong&gt;means having the power to cause changes or having a significant impact on someone or something.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;So when we say a novel is one of the most influential pieces of literature, it signifies that the novel has had a substantial effect on English literature in some way.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore, the completed sentence reads:&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;This novel is one of the most influential pieces of literature in the history of the English language.&amp;quot;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Option 2&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;Forgettable&amp;#39;: This contradicts the notion of the novel being one of the most significant in history.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;Obscure&amp;#39;: This implies the novel is not well known or significant, which again contradicts the notion of the novel being one of the most notable in history.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;Outdated&amp;#39;: This suggests the novel is no longer relevant or valuable, which doesn&amp;#39;t match the intended significance of the novel implied in the sentence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;tranquil.&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Tranquil&amp;#39; &lt;/strong&gt;refers to a state that is calm, peaceful, and quiet.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;It fits well in this context because it describes the ideal environment for studying.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore, &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;tranquil&amp;#39; &lt;/strong&gt;best describes the type of haven that a library provides for students.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The completed sentence reads:
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;quot;The quiet corners of the library provide a tranquil haven for students who wish to study in peace.&amp;quot;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Option 3&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;Noisy&amp;#39;: This means full of noise, loud, which opposes the idea of a peaceful studying environment.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;Tumultuous&amp;#39;: This means making a lot of noise, being excited, confused, or disorderly, which contradicts the desired peacefulness in studying.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;Agitating&amp;#39;: This suggests something causing trouble or annoyance, and does not align with the intent of a quiet place for focus and study.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The correct answer is &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;ironed out&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The phrase &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;ironed out&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot; means to resolve or clear up (a problem or difficulty). (समस्या हल करना)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The driver subtly resolved the issue related to the traffic violation he committed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The other options: &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;ironed through&lt;/strong&gt;,&amp;quot; &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;ironed in&lt;/strong&gt;,&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;ironed aside&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot; do not fit the context as appropriately.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;​Therefore, the correct answer is &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Option 3&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complete Sentence:&lt;/strong&gt; The driver very subtly &lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;ironed out&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt; the traffic violation he committed.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ironed through&lt;/strong&gt;: not a commonly used phrasal verb in this context.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ironed in&lt;/strong&gt;: typically means to press into fabric, not applicable here. (कपड़े में दबाना)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ironed aside&lt;/strong&gt;: not a standard phrasal verb in English.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
